        <abstract> 
<p>Mentions his paper ["Transportal of erratic boulders", <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 1: 218–27]. Discusses ice-borne rock. Reference to unpublished paper on icebergs [?"Power of icebergs to make grooves", <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 1: 252–5]. Remarks on scoring by icebergs. Comments on judgment of theories by Geological Society.</p> 
        </abstract>
